    "name": "Dicey Tales",
    "steam_appid": 3279980,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏信息</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Dicey Tales》是一款 <strong>受桌游启发的卡组构筑类RPG</strong>。<br>投掷骰子攻击敌人，预测他们的行动，制定最佳战术！<br>在冒险中招募队友，书写属于你的传奇故事。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dice + Tactics</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279980/extras/14a0150f1cc34bd932704ad30f003fb0.poster.avif?t=1770985666\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279980/extras/14a0150f1cc34bd932704ad30f003fb0.webm?t=1770985666\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279980/extras/14a0150f1cc34bd932704ad30f003fb0.mp4?t=1770985666\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  战斗发生在 <strong>7×7 的棋盘</strong> 上。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用骰子移动英雄，攻击敌人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279980/extras/a533b42449977b30cd32630327341140.poster.avif?t=1770985666\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279980/extras/a533b42449977b30cd32630327341140.webm?t=1770985666\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279980/extras/a533b42449977b30cd32630327341140.mp4?t=1770985666\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >组合骰子的点数，释放强大的技能！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279980/extras/43dd4551bd94729fb5c819f173f89f57.poster.avif?t=1770985666\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279980/extras/43dd4551bd94729fb5c819f173f89f57.webm?t=1770985666\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279980/extras/43dd4551bd94729fb5c819f173f89f57.mp4?t=1770985666\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有时候，危机也是机会——利用敌人的攻击策略，反败为胜！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>18位独特英雄与技能组合</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279980/extras/028921f06cdda28fc092cd8131e0b6a5.poster.avif?t=1770985666\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279980/extras/028921f06cdda28fc092cd8131e0b6a5.webm?t=1770985666\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279980/extras/028921f06cdda28fc092cd8131e0b6a5.mp4?t=1770985666\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >招募并培养 18位风格各异的英雄。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279980/extras/2907e2576262cb5fa19b370bcf852a01.avif?t=1770985666\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279980/extras_big/2907e2576262cb5fa19b370bcf852a01.avif?t=1770985666 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个英雄都有独特的技能树和战斗定位。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >运用他们的特殊技能，使战斗充满变化与深度。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >英雄之间还能形成 <strong>强大的协同效应</strong>——推开敌人、点燃战场、冻结战局！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>世界与事件</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279980/extras/0e412eae02e57b579f2d461075e11751.poster.avif?t=1770985666\" width=800 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279980/extras/0e412eae02e57b579f2d461075e11751.webm?t=1770985666\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279980/extras/0e412eae02e57b579f2d461075e11751.mp4?t=1770985666\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索一个充满故事的 奇幻世界，这里的每个英雄、村民，甚至一只小恶魔都有自己的故事。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279980/extras/db534099d67b74a61a4e1533f6c91be3.poster.avif?t=1770985666\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279980/extras/db534099d67b74a61a4e1533f6c91be3.webm?t=1770985666\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279980/extras/db534099d67b74a61a4e1533f6c91be3.mp4?t=1770985666\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >了解他们的故事，将他们纳入你的队伍！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279980/extras/0c42857257f34c9efa439278283cbb49.poster.avif?t=1770985666\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279980/extras/0c42857257f34c9efa439278283cbb49.webm?t=1770985666\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279980/extras/0c42857257f34c9efa439278283cbb49.mp4?t=1770985666\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >投掷骰子，决定你的命运。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279980/extras/04482f98074d461a83c44d50adef53fc.poster.avif?t=1770985666\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279980/extras/04482f98074d461a83c44d50adef53fc.webm?t=1770985666\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279980/extras/04482f98074d461a83c44d50adef53fc.mp4?t=1770985666\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >寻找 女神雕像 以获得祝福并强化你的骰子！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>遗物</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279980/extras/4e07762c08f55a5dfdee95506b7bac77.poster.avif?t=1770985666\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279980/extras/4e07762c08f55a5dfdee95506b7bac77.webm?t=1770985666\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279980/extras/4e07762c08f55a5dfdee95506b7bac77.mp4?t=1770985666\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >各种拥有独特效果的遗物 将帮助你定义战术风格。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >收集遗物，增强英雄能力，解锁新的战斗方式！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>英雄传记</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279980/extras/1ec7a497b31474e06b453b6b5f35b93d.avif?t=1770985666\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3279980/extras_big/1ec7a497b31474e06b453b6b5f35b93d.avif?t=1770985666 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >积累经验值，强化英雄传记。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >让你的队伍变得更强，并解锁新的 初始英雄！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
